tip.text: Delicious crêperie! I ordered the one with Raspberries and white chocolate: just divine!
We chose Saturday for lunch as they serve the "Duck & Champagne" set menu-absolutely delicious and good value for money! Duck was simply amazing and we also love the atmsphere.
Amazing sushi and very cool vibes! I suggest it for a special occasion with the partner, or with a small group of close friends.
Ottimo ristorante che offre piatti di pesce fresco, cucinato con semplicità secondo la tradizione veneta. Chiedete al cameriere il pesce del giorno e vi consiglierà il meglio.
Ricotta pancakes are delicious but the portion is too big for 1 person: better to have a salty dish and theb order pancakes as a dessert to share.
Great location, nice rooms, fast internet. Cool vibes from restaurant and bar. I definitely recommend it!
Fichi with ricotta and honey, and Strozzapreti "cacio e pepe": the perfect dinner at this lovely Italian place!
My healthy and light suggestion is definitely the Seared tina dish with soba noodles: you'll love it! And keep some space for thr Flourless chocolate cake...just yummy!
